{"tid":665550,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(棒球有圖) 上一壘問題","createTime":"2018-05-15T05:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T05:58:46.000Z","uid":133727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"09791d9c0237d67b7afcda82d68d3f26822237c4","tid":665550,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/130011_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F130011_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b7141348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑色線係batter (runner)<br />\n藍色線係個ball<br />\n<br />\n假設batter 打到個地波<br />\n佢向一疊狗衝<br />\n<br />\npitcher 接到個波傳比一壘<br />\n<br />\nrunner 係波到前踏到一壘<br />\n但係佢狗衝得太快過左龍<br />\n<br />\n係佢回一壘前個波已經到左一壘手手上<br />\n<br />\n如圖顯示runner 當時唔係壘上, 而係一壘後少少<br />\n<br />\n咁我想問呢個時候一壘手可唔可以觸殺個 runner呢？"},{"pid":"c04374a3b02d8e4757b14c7f82371f3fbd70db5b","tid":665550,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"應該得,但係真係咁做就變左不君子行為(好似係) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adaa6144f8f0f1d78fd6ebae02f4f295026b4f8d","tid":665550,"uid":45968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"上一壘可以沖過壘包，只要你冇意識上二壘，就唔會造成觸殺"},{"pid":"0431c4ecf1508f7f5e25765ec88c3d2a44f67744","tid":665550,"uid":133727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adaa6144f8f0f1d78fd6ebae02f4f295026b4f8d","tid":665550,"uid":45968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"上一壘可以沖過壘包，只要你冇意識上二壘，就唔會造成觸殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:12:26.000Z","msg":"明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁二壘同三壘都係一樣？"},{"pid":"f1d3bf63b61ca5d540008a67e18228241444d4a2","tid":665550,"uid":45968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05